comments: McConnell (IND) moves laterally into Brunson's (NYK) path and initiates body contact that affects his SQBR during the drive.
Bitadze (IND) briefly places his left arm on Robinson's (NYK) body and marginal contact occurs as he simultaneously deflects the pass.
Barrett (NYK) slightly jumps alongside Hield (IND) and marginal body contact occurs after the release of the driving shot attempt.
Bitadze (IND) establishes himself in Barrett's (NYK) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Barrett (NYK) makes contact with Hield's (IND) arm during the release of his jump shot attempt.
Bitadze (IND) extends his leg and he kicks the ball during Brunson's (NYK) dribble.
Bitadze (IND) touches the ball last before going out of bounds.
Randle (NYK) briefly places a hand on Hield's (IND) body and then immediately removes it, as Hield begins his upward shooting motion. The contact that occurs is marginal.
Bitadze (IND) swipes up and marginal arm contact occurs with Randle (NYK) as they come together during the trap.
Nembhard (IND) commits a take foul on Barrett (NYK).
Mathurin (IND) splits his feet at the start of his dribble.
Brunson (NYK) moves alongside Mathurin's (IND) path and marginal body contact occurs during the driving shot attempt.
After the made basket, Grimes (NYK) interferes with the ball and prevents it from promptly being put back into play.
